data.title: Fun For All
data.text: Had a little bit of everything going on Friday, must say they kept us entertained. The little waitress that's from Alabama was excellent, she worked extra hard and was extra funny.

data.title: "Friends" and "Cheers" rolled into one.
data.text: Really have a great space that is inviting and functional. Love the outdoor balcony area... really takes the place to a new level from some other past locations in Sioux Falls.  Always a friendly face, to welcome you back, and an open atmosphere to enjoy the music and special events that are usually posted.
